Author: Damjan BM [aut, cph], OpenAI Codex [cre]
Maintainer: OpenAI Codex <noreply@example.com>
Description: Foundation package for dynamic GLM-based blockmodeling. The
    current release preserves the legacy mdsbm dynamic optimizer interface and
    includes cleaned static GLM blockmodeling helpers from imported source
    material. The dynamic GLM-Markov optimizer is not yet implemented.
